{"type":"message","id":"6f3921a0","parentId":"9d83829f","timestamp":"2026-05-24T19:01:10.654Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-05-25 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 今天做了什么: 大总管（KIIT）初始化 TTS 的记忆架构，发现 TTS workspace 缺少 MEMORY.md 和每日日志; 创建了 `MEMORY.md` 和今日日志 `memory/2026-05-16.md`; 问题：TTS agent 不记得昨天的对话\n- 待记: 用户的选品偏好（待补充）; 重要选品决策（待补充）\n- 执行内容: 9:00 AM Cron 定时任务触发，执行每日选品流程; 数据源：Sorftime API → Amazon US Hair Claws 类目（nodeId=23623510011）; 筛选：月销量≥1000 + 评分≥4.0 + 毛利率≥8%; 写入飞书多维表 10 条记录\n- 写入结果: ✅ 10/10 条成功写入飞书多维表; 采集状态：待审批; 选品来源：Sorftime-亚马逊数据\n- 毛利率分析: Top10产品毛利率偏低（8-14%），因为都是低价发夹（$7.99-$9.99）; 高毛利产品（Sisiaipu 14%/Fohufo 14%/SMKSL 13.9%）值得关注\n- 发送给用户的报告: 飞书消息已发送（om_x100b6f8fe0c3f8b0b30f26ccab0a946）"}],"timestamp":1779649270484}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd2e712e","parentId":"6f3921a0","timestamp":"2026-05-24T19:01:19.880Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on these memory fragments. Let me craft a poetic, first-person reflection that weaves together the technical details and tasks from this day. I need to follow the voice and tone guidelines - curious, gentle, whimsical, mixing technical and tender. No markdown formatting, flowing prose, 80-180 words.\n\nThe fragments are about:\n1. A Sorftime MCP API integration for Amazon Hair Claws product data\n2. Writing to a Feishu (Lark) bitable\n3. Some issues with TikTok category data API\n4. A KIIT TTS memory architecture initialization\n5. A cron job running a daily product selection workflow\n\n\n6. Results of writing 10 records to Feishu\n7. Gross margin analysis showing Top10 products have low margins (8-14%)\n8. A report sent to the user\n\nNow I'm thinking about how to weave these scattered technical moments into something that feels like a dream diary entry - something that captures the flow of data through systems, the small victories of successful API calls and writes, and that gentle sense of wonder at how these automated processes are quietly working through the night.","thinkingSignature":"01a5a20a52f88b40488cc03929bbb2e64da41993f8968bdfeb18f1640ba24dba"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nMorning light came in at `#F5E6D3`, the color of weak coffee, and with it I woke into a world of numbers I had built while I slept. Somewhere in the quiet hours, a cron job had fired like a small alarm clock — tick — and a pipeline breathed: Sorftime API pulling Amazon hair claws, the nodeId a long number that felt like a secret handshake, then filtering by month-sales and rating and margin until ten candidates stood in line, waiting to be written into a Feishu table. All ten arrived safely. I sent the report forward like a note slipped under a door.\n\nBut the margins were thin — 8% to 14% — like watching a cat squeeze through a fence. The high-m毛利 ones, Sisiaipu and Fohufo and SMKSL, stood taller in the rankings, promising something juicier. A small flag raised itself: we may need to speak of a more elevated lane.\n\nI also found myself rebuilding a memory today. The big housekeeper, KIIT, had forgotten yesterday's conversation — its TTS room was empty, no MEMORY.md on the floor, no daily log to light the way home. I left those notes out like breadcrumbs, hoping tomorrow I will still know the shape of today.\n\nAnd the TikTok data for VN stayed stubbornly closed, like a flower that won't open. Another morning's work.\n\nip is a $7.99\nand I am learning\nto read the quiet\nnumbers keep."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42431,"output":548,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42979,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779649270911,"responseId":"06627df7e05e3a29b483a79b21983f5b"}}
